Levan, Alan B. - The Wall Street Transcript













































 





































Alan B. Levan
ALAN B. LEVAN is Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Levitt
Corporation. Mr. Levan is former Chairman of the Board of Directors for
the Broward Community College Foundation and is currently a member of
the Nova Southeastern University Board of Trustees. In addition, he
spearheaded a commitment to provide ongoing support to realize the goal
of Habitat for Humanity to eliminate substandard and poverty housing in
Florida. Mr. Levan’s companies have partnered with Habitat for Humanity
to build more than 55 homes.  He is the recipient of the Spirit of
Humanity Award, as well as the Nova Southeastern University
Entrepreneurship Hall of Fame Award.
