Bluegreen Corp. »
Bluegreen Corp. develops, manages and sells timeshare resorts and residential land. It markets residential land home sites to retail customers who seek to build a home in a residential setting, including on properties featuring a golf course and related amenities. The firm operates through various segments that include Bluegreen Resorts and Bluegreen Communities. The Bluegreen Resorts segment markets, sells and manages real estate-based vacation ownership interests in resorts while the Bluegreen Communities segment acquires, develops and subdivides properties. The company was founded ion September 18, 1985 and is headquartered in Boca Raton, FL.






